<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1908/512406-625x325.jpg?2" alt="Image credit: Alex Suprun on Unsplash." width="625" height="325">Image credit: Alex Suprun on Unsplash.“The effect of adding a powerhouse like BMW Group SA to our stable is incalculable in terms of the energy it releases within the agency. This is not only because of its global iconic status, but also because its brands match our vision.This is a company that is constantly reinventing its brands and taking the future head-on. This could just as easily be me talking about us. This is one of those times I am delighted that you are judged by the company you keep,” says Haydn Townsend, group CEO of Wunderman Thompson.